message.body: Hello! How's it going?
Yoyo! Good at a coffeeshop and you?
Now I'm at work...woohoo.
Nice - what do you do
Performance art, acting, singin....rando jobs to support art..you?
That's awesome - in philly? I work for a health care improvement non profit
We try and find the best healthcare ideas and spread them worldwide
That's awesome, the world needs them!! :) seriously. Such a serious issue. Affects everyone.
Yeah, it's been a great place to work. Do you live in philly?
Yeah been here for a minute. Like 4 years now yikes. You?
I went to school in philly - moved to boston after graduation. I miss philly so much - do you think it's a good art scene?
Ahh yes. I'm in theater and weird performance art and its cool cause its a relatively small community..also cheap to live of course haha
How's boston? (Broad question..ha!)
That's great - what kind of performance art? Have you seen philadanco perform?
Boston is decent - it's crazy expensive, but there are a good amount of jobs and social services. It's not diverse/integrated enough though - it's a veryterritorial place
ahhhh I see, I was there once for a conference..women action and the media it was held at the frank ghery building which was soo coooool :)
Nice, I really like gehry - he just finished an alzheimers research building in Las Vegas
Ooh I'm about to head there in a few weeks...sisters are in southern utah so I fly into vegas to see em
Nice - are you heading straight to Utah? Or spending some time in las Vegas too?
Just gonna stay at my cousins, she lives there for work....not a huge fan of vegas but I'm sure ill have fun ha
It's got a lot to offer as a town - head downtown to Fremont - eat at le thai
